Hello, thank you for calling NoteWorthy Music School! My name is Russell Cook. May I know your name, please?

Hi Russell, I'm Evelyn Torres.

It's nice to meet you, Evelyn. How can I assist you today?

I had a few questions about my billing statement.

Of course, I'd be happy to help with that. Could you please provide your account number? It's typically six digits long.

Sure, it's one two three four five six.

Thank you, Evelyn. I have your account details here. Can you also confirm your billing zip code for verification?

Yes, it's nine zero one two zero.

Great, thank you. I've verified your account. Now, what specific billing details would you like to discuss?

I noticed I was charged twice for this month's tuition and wanted to clarify why that occurred.

I see the issue here, Evelyn. It looks like there was a duplicate transaction. We'll reverse the extra charge within the next three to five business days.

Thank you for clearing that up, Russell.

You're welcome, Evelyn. Is there anything else I can help you with today?

No, that's all for now. Thanks for your help.

Thank you for your time, Evelyn. Have a great day!
